<h2 id="ising-model-in-d--0">Ising Model in <em>d</em> = 0</h2>
<p>Let’s consider a system with only two degrees of freedom, which we’ll call $s_1$ and $s_2$.  They are <em>spins</em>, so they only take on the values $s = 1$ and $s = -1$.</p>

